				<dl> 
					<dt>Did you know?</dt> 
					<dd>
						<p>Alexander Bell added his middle name when he was 11 years old. 'Graham' was the surname of a family friend.</p> 
						<p>Helen Keller was one of Bell's most famous pupils. When he started as a tutor, she was a young child who could not see, hear or speak.</p> 
					</dd> 
				</dl> 
